data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Dawsonville, GA! This stunning Cape Cod-style residence offers the perfect blend of charm, convenience, and comfort, all within close proximity to the Outlet Mall and GA 400. Situated on a sprawling 1-acre lot, this property boasts a meticulously landscaped and fully fenced yard, providing ample space for outdoor activities and entertaining. Step onto the expansive front porch, ideal for enjoying your morning coffee or unwinding in the evening. As you enter, you're greeted by a bright and airy interior featuring a spacious white kitchen adorned with granite countertops. The main level also includes a large master bedroom complete with a tiled shower and double sink vanity, and his and hers closets. Upstairs, you'll find generously sized bedrooms, perfect for accommodating family and guests. The versatility of the basement allows for endless possibilities - whether it's utilized as a fourth bedroom with a closet, an office, a playroom, or any other space tailored to your needs. Step outside onto the expansive back deck overlooking the picturesque surroundings, with an additional patio underneath, providing the perfect setting for outdoor entertaining. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful residence your own - schedule your private showing today and experience the epitome of comfortable living in Dawsonville, GA!
